{"tid":1542592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［831太子站恐襲］查有冇死到人係重要 但後續黨鐵CCTV問題係咪都要留意下","createTime":"2019-09-05T01:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:33:24.000Z","uid":253772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7694842a4f142a0dd39ae9e3c361b532649382f9","tid":1542592,"uid":253772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:54:48.000Z","msg":"我知大家仲關心緊當晚有冇死人，<br />\n但手足係咪要考慮下以後喺黨鐵站打爆cam嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831太子站記者比狗趕哂出黎，無人知當晚站入面發生咩事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵未必會交CCTV一回事，但自己人打爛咗無哂證據又另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一日有片都有可能比人搵到出黎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我無能力無膽上前線，831個日出完銅鑼灣充下人數留到8點幾就開始走，<br />\n去到旺角站月台9點半度啦，見到有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2個人</span></span>騎膊馬打爛緊Cam，個刻我都無乜特別感覺，純粹諗住打爛咗之後前線走唔洗比人影到，<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但一番到屋企就睇到太子站恐襲喇DLLM</span></span><br />\n之後呢幾日開始日日有人手動轉要黨鐵交CCTV，就心諗會唔會太子都真係比人打爆埋交唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我睇唔到太子站有冇cam被打爛，但前晚喺黃大仙站都見真係有手足會爆cam，比記者影到，我喺now tv news睇到嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵有片都可以屈我地破壞咗無片啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n以後有咩行動係咪應該諗諗唔係所有cam都可以打爛，無咗cam，無埋記者班狗喺站入面真係做乜鳩都無人知架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼不嬲都有，但我知唔係有呢啲情景出現就要話係鬼做，<span style=\"color: violet;\">不分化不割蓆，做法唔完美但可接受</span>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我亦理解破壞黨鐵站嘅意義何在</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但呢個po只係針對CCTV啫</span></span><br />\n如果真係有手足要咁做嘅，第時諗諗cam嘅所在地爆唔爆得過先好嘛？又，如果見到有人咁做都諗諗洗唔洗阻止好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP牌第一次認真開po，認同請幫推（諗緊係咪自己都推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），有唔啱請指證，唔好屌得咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前晚半夜3點開完 無乜人睇到開多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c7540afd72533132c52b222d727570c51ab241","tid":1542592,"uid":253772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:57:06.000Z","msg":"自推下先 雖然都唔知p牌得唔得"},{"pid":"e45885e78f9a74ffaf67ffd993bb046b61a6e5c2","tid":1542592,"uid":253772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:57:22.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c072abf75f333668d7a18b42be013e4050bb2543","tid":1542592,"uid":253772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:57:56.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"4175daedbd808e38171e47b2e77de941fafbd315","tid":1542592,"uid":253772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c4f8fe06767eb4f394dacf52cde4688423ba1d96","tid":1542592,"uid":253772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:58:17.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5ff9ad2c1005e2b6c8a4703ed9ddb6bfa18dbccd","tid":1542592,"uid":253772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T0